name: FNF - Vs. Yoshi Full Week
description:
Somehow you end up in an island falling down. Your girlfriend although managed to get caught in a basket, knocking off one of the babies that was in there. You land in the grass, and start panicking, up until you see a green dinosaur heading towards your way.

This mod includes a new week 3 songs with just a singular character for now, with more updates coming in the future.
